Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.72,0:23:25.00,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,早上好 阿贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.09,0:23:27.93,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.81,0:23:31.85,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.27,0:23:34.48,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:36.85,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,今天别翘课哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.15,0:23:38.61,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,到底要不要翘呢~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.61,0:23:39.44,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,喂

